<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blog Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/singleBlogStyle.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include("./components/navbar") %>

        <div class="main-content">
            <h1>Welcome to My Blog</h1>
            <h2>Title: <span>
                    <%= singleBlog[0].title %>
                </span></h2>
            <h3>Subtitle: <span>
                    <%= singleBlog[0].subtitle %>
                </span></h3>
            <h3>Auther: <span>
                    <%= singleBlog[0].user.username %>
                </span></h3>
            <h3>Image: <img src="<%= singleBlog[0].image  %>" alt="image not found" height="200px" width="200px" /></h3>
            <p>Description: <span>
                    <%= singleBlog[0].description %>
                </span></p>
            <p>Aliquam erat volutpat. Fusce euismod, turpis sed sollicitudin elementum, velit est feugiat sem, nec
                fermentum odio ligula a erat. Donec non dolor ut nisi placerat malesuada sit amet eu arcu.</p>
            <% if(currentUser){ %>
                <% if(currentUserId==singleBlog[0].user.id){ %>
                    <button><a href="/delete/<%= singleBlog[0].id  %>">Delete</a></button>
                    <button><a href="/edit/<%= singleBlog[0].id %>">Update</a></button>
                    <% }} %>

        </div>

</body>

</html>